

{"id":1968,"date":"2022-03-22T14:23:43","date_gmt":"2022-03-22T13:23:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/?page_id=1968"},"modified":"2022-11-03T21:31:09","modified_gmt":"2022-11-03T20:31:09","slug":"reinscription","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/reinscription\/","title":{"rendered":"R\u00e9inscription"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"has-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\"><strong>Condition de r\u00e9inscription<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>La r\u00e9inscription est accord\u00e9e aux candidats n&#8217;ayant pas interrompue leurs inscriptions. Dans le cas contraire, ils doivent d\u00e9poser une demande de r\u00e9int\u00e9gration accompagn\u00e9e des justificatifs de l&#8217;interruption des inscriptions pr\u00e9c\u00e9dentes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"has-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\"><strong>Dossier de r\u00e9inscription<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Une demande d&#8217;inscription&nbsp;(<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Demande-dinscription-Doctorat.docx\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Demande-dinscription-Doctorat.docx\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a>)<\/li><li>Une autorisation d&#8217;inscription en post-graduation&nbsp;(<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Autorisation-dinscription-en-Post-Graduation-Doctorat.docx\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Autorisation-dinscription-en-Post-Graduation-Doctorat.docx\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a>)<\/li><li>Une demande d&#8217;inscription pour les candidats hors USTHB&nbsp;(<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Demande-dinscription-HORS-USTHB-pour-les-travailleurs.docx\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Demande-dinscription-HORS-USTHB-pour-les-travailleurs.docx\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a>)<\/li><li>Un descriptif de l\u2019\u00e9tat d\u2019avancement de la th\u00e8se de Doctorat (Pour le Doctorant)(<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Etat-avancement-doctorat-canevas.docx\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Etat-avancement-doctorat-canevas.docx\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a>)<\/li><li>Un extrait du P.V du conseil Scientifique&nbsp;<strong>en cas de changement de sujet ou de Directeur de m\u00e9moire ou de th\u00e8se<\/strong>.<\/li><li>Deux photographies d&#8217;identit\u00e9<\/li><li>Une d\u00e9claration sur l&#8217;honneur pour les \u00e9tudiants n&#8217;exer\u00e7ant aucune activit\u00e9 r\u00e9mun\u00e9r\u00e9e&nbsp;(<a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Declaration-sur-lhonneur-Pour-les-non-Travailleurs.docx\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Declaration-sur-lhonneur-Pour-les-non-Travailleurs.docx\">T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/a>)<\/li><li>Une attestation de fonction pour l&#8217;ann\u00e9e universitaire en cours<\/li><li>Une fiche d&#8217;\u00e9tat civil en cas de changement d&#8217;\u00e9tat civil.<\/li><li>R\u00e9c\u00e9piss\u00e9 portant paiement des droits d&#8217;inscription 200 DA (pour les candidats hors USTHB, et pour ceux qui n&#8217;exercent pas une fonction r\u00e9mun\u00e9r\u00e9e).<\/li><\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Condition de r\u00e9inscription La r\u00e9inscription est accord\u00e9e aux candidats n&#8217;ayant pas interrompue leurs inscriptions. Dans le cas contraire, ils doivent <span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/reinscription\/\">Suite<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1968","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links